  # Made by Google 2024 Live Blog + News Hub: Pixel 9, Pixel Watch 3, and more
  
  [![Avatar for Abner Li](https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d8da06fcba2b80ec1f2d301d7376dae8e055ac48d88994a8042b1d6b2c352534?s=30&d=mm&r=r)](https://9to5google.com/author/technacity/) [Abner Li](https://9to5google.com/author/technacity/ "Posts by Abner Li") \| Aug 13 2024 - 9:47 am PT
  
