  on-device model, Gemini Nano with Multimodality.
  Thanks to this powerful on-device infrastructure, nearly
  every experience across the phone is powered by AI,
  including unique features we've developed just for Pixel.
  Today, we're going to show you new ways that on-device AI is
  improving your phone calls... New Gemini-powered features to
  help you be more organized, or be more creative...
  And of course, new Pixel Camera features that help you get the
  perfect photo or video. But let's start with Pixel 9's
  new look, our biggest Pixel design progression in years.
  We have four new phones, including the gorgeous new Pixel
  9, and the reimagined Pixel 9 Pro Fold.
  And we've heard from Pixel users that just because they want a
  pro phone, doesn't necessarily mean they want a big phone.
  So for the first time, you can choose between Pixel 9 Pro and
  Pixel 9 Pro XL, without compromises.
  [ Cheers and Applause ] They have the same incredible
  display, sleek design, premium craftsmanship, processing power,
  and the same Pro Pixel Camera. All of our new Pixel 9 phones
  feature a completely re-engineered, sculpted design
