  hand, compactness, and durability.
  Thanks to the luxurious metal frame with its seamless rounded
  corners, and the scratch-resistant, flat Gorilla
  Glass Victus 2, the Pixel 9 phones are twice as durable as
  the previous generation, to withstand the inevitable
  accidental drops. Pixel 9 has an even brighter
  Actua display, and the Pro models use our Super Actua
