  8's peak rate with Gemini Nano. We've also upgraded the memory
  across the entire Pixel 9 family...
  With 12 gigabytes of RAM for Pixel 9...
  And the Pro models come with 16 gigabytes.
  Put simply, Tensor, Gemini Nano, and your phone's memory work
